snippet.title: Zero Caliber 2 - Official Trailer VR Game
snippet.description: Take a glimpse at action-packed gameplay and more in this trailer for Zero Caliber 2, an upcoming follow-up to the VR FPS game Zero Caliber from XREAL Games. Zero Caliber 2 will be available in 2024 on Meta Quest and Steam VR.
